script.name: plugin.loadoutm.viewmenu
script.sourceplaintext:
$page.id = get global variable: name='pageid.guilds'
$TEXT.NONE = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=689
$HQ = get player HQ $loadout.id = get global variable: name='loadout.id'
if $a.event == [MEvent.Start] $loadout.id = $a.data set global variable: name='loadout.id' value=$loadout.id gosub sub.BuildMenu return $input
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Select] $menu.id = $a.data[0] $selection = $a.data[1] if $menu.id == 'loadout.viewmenu' if $selection == 'apply.setting' play sample [Sound.Success] $flags = [Loadout.Settings] | [Loadout.Lasers] @ = $a.obj -> call script lib.cycrow.applyloadout : HQ=$HQ Loadout ID=$loadout.id Loadout Flags=$flags Buy Upgprades?=[FALSE] gosub sub.BuildMenu $input = create input return value: update menu=$menu return $input end end
else if $a.event == 'loadout.viewmenu' if $a.data == 'apply' START $a.obj -> delayed command COMMAND_SHIP_LOADOUT : arg1=$HQ, arg2=$loadout.id, arg3=null, arg4=null START speak text: page=[Page.MiscVoice] id=131 priority=20 end
else if $a.event == [MEvent.Finished] set global variable: name='loadout.id' value=null end
return null
sub.AddWare: $sub.got.amt = $total.wares[$ware] skip if $sub.got.amt $sub.got.amt = 0 $sub.got.amt = $sub.got.amt + $sub.amt $total.wares[$ware] = $sub.got.amt endsub
sub.BuildMenu: if $a.obj -> exists $edge = 200 else $edge = 0 end
$errors = 0
$loadout.name = $HQ ->get HQ loadout name: id=$loadout.id $loadout.type = $HQ ->get HQ loadout type: id=$loadout.id
$menu = create custom menu array
$total.wares = table alloc
if $a.obj -> exists $text.cols = array alloc: size=3 $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=4768 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=100 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[0] = $text $pos = -1 - $edge $read.text = read text: page=6020 id=2022 $text = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[1] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=100 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=$edge right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[2] = $text else $text.cols = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=4768 end add info line heading to menu: $menu, heading=$text.cols $wares = $HQ ->get HQ loadout wares: id=$loadout.id flags=[Loadout.Shields]
$shield.bays = get max shield number: shiptype=$loadout.type $bay = 0
$shield.i = get number of subtypes of maintype [SSTYPE_SHIELD] while $shield.i dec $shield.i = $shield = get ware from maintype [SSTYPE_SHIELD] and subtype $shield.i $amt = $wares[$shield] while $amt > 0 do if $bay >= $shield.bays break dec $amt = inc $bay =
$ware = $shield $sub.amt = 1 gosub sub.AddWare
$text.cols = array alloc: size=3 $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=698 $text = sprintf: fmt='%s %s', $read.text, $bay, null, null, null $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=100 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[0] = $text $pos = -1 - $edge $text = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$shield $text.cols[1] = $text $col = [MenuColour.Normal] if $a.obj -> exists $tmp = $bay - 1 $text = $a.obj -> get shield type in bay $tmp if not $text $text = $TEXT.NONE $col = [MenuColour.Red] else if $shield != $text $col = [MenuColour.Red] end else $text = ' ' end do if $col == [MenuColour.Red] inc $errors = $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=$col text=$text $text.cols[2] = $text add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text.cols end end
while $bay < $shield.bays inc $bay =
$text.cols = array alloc: size=3 $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=698 $text = sprintf: fmt='%s %s', $read.text, $bay, null, null, null $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=100 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[0] = $text $pos = -1 - $edge $text = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$TEXT.NONE $text.cols[1] = $text $col = [MenuColour.Normal] if $a.obj -> exists $tmp = $bay - 1 $text = $a.obj -> get shield type in bay $tmp if not $text $text = $TEXT.NONE else $col = [MenuColour.Red] end else $text = ' ' end do if $col == [MenuColour.Red] inc $errors = $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=$col text=$text $text.cols[2] = $text
add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text.cols end
$weapons = $HQ ->get HQ loadout weapon order: id=$loadout.id if $weapons
if $a.obj -> exists $text.cols = array alloc: size=3 $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=9114 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=100 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[0] = $text $pos = -1 - $edge $read.text = read text: page=6020 id=2022 $text = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[1] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3040 $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=$edge right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[2] = $text else $text.cols = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=9114 end add info line heading to menu: $menu, heading=$text.cols
$size = size of array $weapons $i = 0 while $i < $size $weapon.array = $weapons[$i] $turret.name = get turret text: shiptype=$loadout.type turret=$i $size.j = size of array $weapon.array $j = 0 while $j < $size.j $laser = $weapon.array[$j] inc $j =
$text.cols = array alloc: size=3 $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=698 $text = sprintf: fmt='%s: %s %s', $turret.name, $read.text, $j, null, null $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=100 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[0] = $text $pos = -1 - $edge if $laser == -1 $text = $TEXT.NONE else $ware = $laser $sub.amt = 1 gosub sub.AddWare $text = $laser end $text = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[1] = $text
$col = [MenuColour.Normal] if $a.obj -> exists $tmp = $j - 1 $got.laser = $a.obj -> get laser type in turret $i at slot $tmp if $got.laser $text = $got.laser else $text = $TEXT.NONE end
if $laser != $got.laser do if $laser != -1 OR $got.laser $col = [MenuColour.Red] end else $text = ' ' end do if $col == [MenuColour.Red] inc $errors = $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=$edge right=[TRUE] colour=$col text=$text $text.cols[2] = $text
add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text.cols end add info line section to menu: $menu inc $i = end
end
$heading = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=791 $wares = $HQ ->get HQ loadout wares: id=$loadout.id flags=[Loadout.Upgrade] gosub sub.DisplayWares
$heading = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=792 $wares = $HQ ->get HQ loadout wares: id=$loadout.id flags=[Loadout.Equipment] gosub sub.DisplayWares
$heading = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=9203 $wares = $HQ ->get HQ loadout wares: id=$loadout.id flags=[Loadout.Ammunition] gosub sub.DisplayWares
$heading = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=9113 $wares = $HQ ->get HQ loadout wares: id=$loadout.id flags=[Loadout.Missiles] gosub sub.DisplayWares
$heading = read text: page=[Page.Encyclopedia] id=9 $wares = $HQ ->get HQ loadout wares: id=$loadout.id flags=[Loadout.Other] gosub sub.DisplayWares
$heading = read text: page=2005 id=509 $wares = $HQ ->get HQ loadout resupply: id=$loadout.id gosub sub.DisplayWares
if $a.obj -> exists $text.cols = array alloc: size=3 $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104260 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=100 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[0] = $text $pos = -1 - $edge $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104418 $text = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[1] = $text $read.text = 'Got' $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=$edge right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[2] = $text else $text.cols = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104260 end
add info line heading to menu: $menu, heading=$text.cols $data = $HQ ->get HQ loadout settings: id=$loadout.id if $data skip if size of table $data $data = null end
if not $data add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$TEXT.NONE else @ $ret = [THIS] -> call script plugin.loadoutm.getsettings : Ship Type=$loadout.type $order = $ret[0] $setting.width = $ret[1]
do if $a.obj -> exists $got.settings = $a.obj ->get ship settings table: for loadout=[TRUE]
$i = 0 $size = size of array $order while $i < $size $setting = $order[$i] inc $i = if not $setting add info line section to menu: $menu else $value = $data[$setting] @ $text = [THIS] -> call script lib.cycrow.getloadoutsetting : Setting=$setting Value=$value Ship Type=$loadout.type if $text $text2 = $text[1] $text = $text[0]
$text.cols = array alloc: size=3 $setting.len = $setting.width[$setting] skip if $setting.len $setting.len = 50
$len = 300 - $setting.len $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=$len right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[0] = $text $pos = -1 - $edge $text = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=$setting.len right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text2 $text.cols[1] = $text
$col = [MenuColour.Normal] if $a.obj -> exists $got.value = $got.settings[$setting] @ $text = [THIS] -> call script lib.cycrow.getloadoutsetting : Setting=$setting Value=$got.value Ship Type=$loadout.type $text = $text[1] do if $got.value != $value $col = [MenuColour.Red] else $text = ' ' end do if $col == [MenuColour.Red] inc $errors = $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=$edge right=[TRUE] colour=$col text=$text $text.cols[2] = $text add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text.cols end end end end
$text.cols = array alloc: size=3 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3041 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=200 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[0] = $text $pos = -1 - $edge $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1104418 $text = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[1] = $text if $a.obj -> exists $text = read text: page=$page.id id=3045 else $text = ' ' end $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=$edge right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[2] = $text add info line heading to menu: $menu, heading=$text.cols
if not size of table $total.wares add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$TEXT.NONE else $sorted.array = sort table keys: table=$total.wares $i = 0 $size = size of array $sorted.array while $i < $size $ware = $sorted.array[$i] $amt = $total.wares[$ware]
$text.cols = array alloc: size=3 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=200 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$ware $text.cols[0] = $text $pos = -1 - $edge $text = convert number $amt to string $text = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[1] = $text
$col = [MenuColour.Normal] if $a.obj -> exists $got.amt = $a.obj -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $text = convert number $got.amt to string if $got.amt >= $amt $col = [MenuColour.Green] else $col = [MenuColour.Red] end else $text = ' ' end $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=$edge right=[TRUE] colour=$col text=$text $text.cols[2] = $text add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text.cols inc $i = end end
if $a.obj -> exists if not $errors $text.cols = array alloc: size=2 $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3042 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=200 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[0] = $text $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3047 $text = sprintf: fmt='[%s]', $read.text, null, null, null, null $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=200 right=[TRUE] colour=[MenuColour.Bold] text=$text $text.cols[1] = $text $ret = create menu return value: disabled, id='apply' set menu line option: $menu, selection colour=[MenuColour.Disabled] add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$text.cols returnvalue=$ret else $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3042 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text returnvalue='apply' end $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3046 $ret = create menu return value: callback, value='apply.setting' add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text returnvalue=$ret $read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=3043 add custom menu item to array $menu: text=$read.text returnvalue='close'
set menu option: $menu, page up/down keys for info=[TRUE] $opt = create new array, arguments=-10, 24, 5, null, null append $opt to array $menu else set menu option: $menu, no select lines=[TRUE] end
set menu option: $menu, icon=153 if $a.obj -> exists set menu option: $menu, widthtype=[MenuWidth.Big] else set menu option: $menu, widthtype=[MenuWidth.Standard] end $text = $HQ ->get HQ loadout name: id=$loadout.id $text = sprintf: pageid=$page.id textid=3044, $text, null, null, null, null if $a.obj -> exists $text2 = $a.obj -> get name else $text2 = ' ' end $input = create input: id='loadout.viewmenu' menu=$menu title=$text description=$text2 callback=null endsub
sub.DisplayWares: $COL.TC.LEN = 30 $COL.VOL.LEN = 30 $COL.QTY.LEN = 50
$text.cols = array alloc: size=5 $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=200 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=$heading $text.cols[0] = $text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102518 $pos = -80 - $edge $text = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=$COL.VOL.LEN right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[1] = $text $read.text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102519 $pos = -50 - $edge $text = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=$COL.TC.LEN right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[2] = $text $read.text = read text: page=54 id=30 $pos = -1 - $edge $text = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=$COL.QTY.LEN right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$read.text $text.cols[3] = $text if $a.obj -> exists $text = read text: page=$page.id id=3045 else $text = ' ' end $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=$edge right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[4] = $text add info line heading to menu: $menu, heading=$text.cols
if not size of table $wares add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$TEXT.NONE else $sorted.array = sort table keys: table=$wares $i = 0 $size = size of array $sorted.array while $i < $size $ware = $sorted.array[$i] $amt = $wares[$ware]
$text.cols = array alloc: size=6 $col = [MenuColour.Normal] if is equipment: ware=$ware skip if $HQ -> trades with ware $ware $col = [MenuColour.Red] end $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=-110 right=[FALSE] colour=$col text=$ware $text.cols[0] = $text
if is upgrade: ware=$ware @ $max = [THIS] -> call script lib.cycrow.getupgrademax : Upgrade=$ware Ship Type=$loadout.type $percent = ( $amt * 100 ) / $max $text = create custom menu string progress: width=100 progress=$percent% $pos = -5 - $edge $text = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[1] = $text $text = convert number $amt to string $text2 = convert number $max to string $text = sprintf: fmt='%s / %s', $text, $text2, null, null, null $text = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=100 right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[2] = $text $text = create custom menu column string, position=0 length=0 right=[FALSE] colour=null text=' ' $text.cols[3] = $text if $a.obj -> exists $got.amt = $a.obj -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay $percent = ( $got.amt * 100 ) / $max $text = create custom menu string progress: width=100 progress=$percent% $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=$edge right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[4] = $text $text = convert number $got.amt to string $text2 = convert number $max to string $text = sprintf: fmt='%s / %s', $text, $text2, null, null, null $col = [MenuColour.Normal] skip if $got.amt == $amt $col = [MenuColour.Red] do if $col == [MenuColour.Red] inc $errors = $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=$edge right=[TRUE] colour=$col text=$text $text.cols[5] = $text else $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=$edge right=[TRUE] colour=null text=' ' $text.cols[4] = $text $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=$edge right=[TRUE] colour=null text=' ' $text.cols[5] = $text end else $ware.vol = get volume of ware $ware if is equipment: ware=$ware $ware.flg = get ware flags: ware=$ware skip if $ware.flg & [WareType.EquipVolume] $ware.vol = 0 end if $ware.vol > 0 $text = convert number $ware.vol to string else $text = '-' end $pos = -80 - $edge $text = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=$COL.VOL.LEN right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[1] = $text
$ware.tc = get transport class of ware $ware $text = get short transport class name: class=$ware.tc $pos = -50 - $edge $text = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=$COL.TC.LEN right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[2] = $text
if is single equipment: ware=$ware $text = '-' else $text = convert number $amt to string end $pos = -1 - $edge $text = create custom menu column string, position=$pos length=$COL.QTY.LEN right=[TRUE] colour=null text=$text $text.cols[3] = $text
$col = [MenuColour.Normal] if $a.obj -> exists $got.amt = $a.obj -> get amount of ware $ware in cargo bay if is single equipment: ware=$ware if $got.amt $text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102301 else $text = read text: page=[Page.Menus] id=1102302 end else $text = convert number $got.amt to string end skip if $got.amt == $amt $col = [MenuColour.Red] else $text = ' ' end do if $col == [MenuColour.Red] inc $errors = $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=$edge right=[TRUE] colour=$col text=$text $text.cols[4] = $text $text = create custom menu column string, position=-1 length=$edge right=[TRUE] colour=null text=' ' $text.cols[5] = $text end
add custom menu info line to array $menu: text=$text.cols inc $i = end end endsub
return null
